snippet.title: Cardbob Trailer
snippet.description:
Explore the sci-fi dungeons, collect loot, and negotiate the highest prices in this action roguelite, set in a 3D cardboard world. Grow stronger with each attempt. Be the unlikely hero.

--------------------------------------------------
